name: PornMaster-Fantasy
description:
來自PornMaster的幻想、半寫實版本。使用方式可参考PornMaster。

范例中的"and"，你也可已使用"逗点"，这是我个人习惯的提示词方式。

1.建议Clip跳过层设定为1~2，取样方法Euler a或DPM++ SDE Karras。

2.影响脸部的lora不要使用”面部修复”，例如:cum on face,AHEGAO,tongue out

3.不包括 VAE，但我推荐默认的"vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned"。

4.如果你喜欢我的工作并想支持我： Paypal

我的NSFW作品:https://fansone.co/lala2010360

5..不想要出現太多真實感時，請將"photorealistic"放入負面提示詞中。

6.可用的艺术家姓名。

https://stablediffusion.fr/artists

https://stablediffusion.fr/artist

7..最下方列出可用的攝影師姓名。

Fantasy, semi-realistic version from PornMaster.How to use can refer to PornMaster.

For the "and" in the example, you can also use "comma", this is the prompt word method I am used to.

1.It is recommended to set the clip skip 1~2, the sampling method Euler a or DPM++ SDE Karras.

2.VAE not included but I recommend the default"vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned".

 

3.If you love my work and want to support me:Paypal

My NSFW pieces:https://fansone.co/lala2010360

4.My English is not good, I use Google Translate to talk to you.

5.4.When you don't want too much realism, put "photorealistic" in the negative prompt word.
